# Database & Entity Rules

- All entities inherit `BaseEntity` (`long Id`, audit fields, `IsActive`, `IsDeleted`).
- Fluent API configurations live in `Persistence/Configurations/{Entity}Configuration.cs` — not inline in `OnModelCreating`.
- Unique indexes on soft-deleted entities must be partial: `.HasFilter("\"IsDeleted\" = false")` (for PostgreSQL).
- Read queries: use `.AsNoTracking()` and project with `.Select()` — avoid loading full entities when not needed.
- Global query filters exclude `IsDeleted == true` records by default.
